@page "/product"
@page "/features"
@layout MarketingLayout

<PageTitle>Product &mdash; NavTour</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="NavTour captures your product as live HTML/CSS, turns it into guided interactive demos, and ships buyer analytics, AI drafting, lead forms, and team workflows in one no-code system." />
</HeadContent>

@* ── HERO ── *@
<section class="nt-page-hero">
    <div class="nt-container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Product overview</span>
        <h1>Demo infrastructure for<br /><em>self-serve growth.</em></h1>
        <p class="lead">Capture any web app with the Chrome extension, build guided walkthroughs with the no-code editor, and ship interactive demos that accelerate every stage of the buyer journey.</p>
        <div class="nt-hero-actions">
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-orange btn-lg">Start building free &rarr;</a>
            <a href="/product/ai" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Explore AI features</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* ── OVERVIEW CARDS ── *@
<section class="nt-section">
    <div class="nt-container">
        <div class="nt-card-grid">
            <div class="nt-card">
                <span class="eyebrow">Capture</span>
                <h3>Record the real product</h3>
                <p>One click from the Chrome extension captures your app as live HTML/CSS — not a flat screenshot. Buyers interact with your actual UI, fidelity intact.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-card">
                <span class="eyebrow">Build</span>
                <h3>Layer guided storytelling</h3>
                <p>Add tooltips, hotspots, branching paths, and personalization tokens with a point-and-click editor. No dev tickets, no staging environment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-card">
                <span class="eyebrow">Measure</span>
                <h3>Connect demos to pipeline</h3>
                <p>Step-level analytics, lead capture forms, CRM sync, and team workflows give you the full loop — from first view to signed contract.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* ── FRAMES ── *@
<section class="nt-frames-section">
    <div class="nt-container">
        <div class="nt-section-head">
            <div>
                <span class="num"><b>&sect; 02</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;How it works</span>
                <h2>Four layers, from <em>capture</em> to closed&#x2011;won.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="aside">The product ships as one system — no stitching three point tools together.</div>
        </div>

        <article class="nt-frame-row">
            <div class="nt-frame-copy">
                <div class="num">01<span class="slash">/</span><span class="lbl">Capture</span></div>
                <h3>Browser capture that preserves the app, not just a screenshot.</h3>
                <p>The Chrome extension captures your product as live HTML/CSS with full fidelity. Complex SPAs, dashboards, and auth-gated apps all work — no staging needed.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Click-to-capture workflow, no copy-pasting selectors</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Automatic asset rewriting so the snapshot opens offline</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Works on SPAs, Radzen, and other complex dashboards</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/opgaokkionehglmipncajghhlmohanoi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link-more">Get the extension <span class="ar">&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-frame-visual">
                <span class="nt-frame-cap">Chrome extension &middot; frame 01 of 12</span>
                <div class="nt-frame-img">
                    <img src="/images/shots/editor.png" alt="NavTour demo editor showing captured app" class="nt-lightbox" />
                </div>
                <div class="anno tl">
                    <div class="lbl">Annotation &middot; 01</div>
                    <strong>Live HTML, not a PNG</strong>
                    <p>Hover, click, scroll &mdash; every interaction from the original page still works.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="nt-frame-row reverse">
            <div class="nt-frame-copy">
                <div class="num">02<span class="slash">/</span><span class="lbl">Build</span></div>
                <h3>Layer guided <em>storytelling</em> on top of the real UI.</h3>
                <p>Add tooltips, hotspots, modals, and branching paths with a point-and-click editor. Personalize every demo with tokens like <code style="font-family:var(--nt-mono);font-size:0.88em;background:rgba(251,173,72,0.18);padding:1px 6px;border-radius:4px">&#123;&#123;company&#125;&#125;</code>.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Tooltips, modals, hotspots, spotlight &amp; blur</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Branching paths based on viewer choice</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Real-time collaboration &mdash; multiple editors, one demo</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/product/ai" class="link-more">See AI drafting <span class="ar">&rarr;</span></a>
                <div style="margin-top:18px;font-family:var(--nt-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--nt-muted);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:6px 12px;border:1px solid var(--nt-rule);border-radius:999px">
                    <span style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--nt-orange)"></span>
                    AI drafting by <b style="color:var(--nt-ink);font-weight:600">Anthropic Claude</b>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-frame-visual">
                <span class="nt-frame-cap">Editor &middot; frame 07 of 12</span>
                <div class="nt-frame-img">
                    <img src="/images/shots/player-step1.png" alt="Demo editor with tooltip builder" class="nt-lightbox" />
                </div>
                <div class="anno br">
                    <div class="lbl">Annotation &middot; 02</div>
                    <strong>Branch by buyer persona</strong>
                    <p>Send ops, finance, and IT down different paths &mdash; from the same demo.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="nt-frame-row">
            <div class="nt-frame-copy">
                <div class="num">03<span class="slash">/</span><span class="lbl">Share</span></div>
                <h3>Lead forms, hubs, and branded <em>share links.</em></h3>
                <p>Gate demos with custom lead capture forms, collect them into self-serve Demo Hubs, and send warm showcase links your champions can forward up the buying committee.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Custom lead capture forms attached to any demo</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Embeddable demo hubs for your website or Notion</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Branded showcase links with cover slides and CTAs</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/use-cases" class="link-more">See use cases <span class="ar">&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-frame-visual">
                <span class="nt-frame-cap">Demo Hub &middot; public gallery</span>
                <div class="nt-frame-img">
                    <img src="/images/shots/showcases.png" alt="NavTour showcase links and hub" class="nt-lightbox" />
                </div>
                <div class="anno tr">
                    <div class="lbl">Annotation &middot; 03</div>
                    <strong>Self-serve, always live</strong>
                    <p>Buyers browse and play demos without requesting a rep's time.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="nt-frame-row reverse">
            <div class="nt-frame-copy">
                <div class="num">04<span class="slash">/</span><span class="lbl">Measure</span></div>
                <h3>See exactly where buyers <em>leaned in</em> &mdash; and where they bounced.</h3>
                <p>Step-level analytics, completion funnels, and lead intent signals. Pipe everything into HubSpot, Salesforce, Slack, or your warehouse of choice.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Per-viewer engagement timeline</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Drop-off and completion funnels</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Native CRM + Slack integrations, or raw webhooks</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/integrations" class="link-more">See integrations <span class="ar">&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-frame-visual">
                <span class="nt-frame-cap">Analytics &middot; last 30 days</span>
                <div class="nt-frame-img">
                    <img src="/images/shots/analytics.png" alt="Analytics dashboard" class="nt-lightbox" />
                </div>
                <div class="anno tl">
                    <div class="lbl">Annotation &middot; 04</div>
                    <strong>Intent, not vanity</strong>
                    <p>Who viewed, for how long, which step pushed them to book &mdash; straight into your CRM.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>

<NtCTABand Headline="Start with the shipped product, not a placeholder story."
           SubText="Create a free account and capture your first product flow in under 2 minutes. No credit card, no dev ticket."
           PrimaryLabel="Start free &rarr;"
           SecondaryLabel="Book a walkthrough"
           SecondaryHref="/contact" />
